title: Lisa Ling

description:
Journalist, television personality and author Lisa Ling (Take Out, This is Life with Lisa Ling, National Geographic Explorer, The Oprah Winfrey Show, The View, Our America with Lisa Ling) talks with Anna about courage, her experience in North Korea, human resilience, early loves, meeting her husband, pick-up artist camp, the effects of social media, her new show Take Out on HBO Max and more. Later in the episode, Lisa and Anna talk with a listener who, after a series of bad first-dates, wonders what she can do differently. Their next call is with a listener whose ex-husband’s continued presence in her life is preventing her from moving on.

If you’re in need of some unqualified advice, please write to us at bit.ly/ASKANNA !
